Package logic

Class QuarterReport

java.lang.Object
logic.Report
logic.QuarterReport
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class QuarterReport extends Report
The QuarterReport class represents a report summarizing the daily orders and revenue of a restaurant for a given quarter.
